{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":607,"text":"I had brain surgery 18 years ago,"},{"time":3115,"text":"and since that time, brain science has become"},{"time":5682,"text":"a personal passion of mine."},{"time":7681,"text":"I'm actually an engineer."},{"time":9916,"text":"And first let me say, I recently joined"},{"time":12432,"text":"Google's Moonshot group,"},{"time":13981,"text":"where I had a division,"},{"time":15193,"text":"the display division in Google X,"},{"time":17374,"text":"and the brain science work I'm speaking about today"},{"time":19996,"text":"is work I did before I joined Google"},{"time":22917,"text":"and on the side outside of Google."}]},{"cues":[{"time":25249,"text":"So that said, there's a stigma"},{"time":28432,"text":"when you have brain surgery."},{"time":30717,"text":"Are you still smart or not?"},{"time":33540,"text":"And if not, can you make yourself smart again?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":37388,"text":"After my neurosurgery,"},{"time":39154,"text":"part of my brain was missing,"},{"time":41151,"text":"and I had to deal with that."},{"time":43924,"text":"It wasn't the grey matter, but it \nwas the gooey part dead center"},{"time":46868,"text":"that makes key hormones and neurotransmitters."},{"time":50270,"text":"Immediately after my surgery,"},{"time":52501,"text":"I had to decide what amounts of each of over"},{"time":54644,"text":"a dozen powerful chemicals to take each day,"},{"time":58346,"text":"because if I just took nothing,"},{"time":60155,"text":"I would die within hours."},{"time":62887,"text":"Every day now for 18 years -- every single day --"},{"time":66807,"text":"I've had to try to decide the combinations"},{"time":69517,"text":"and mixtures of chemicals,"},{"time":70845,"text":"and try to get them, to stay alive."},{"time":74692,"text":"There have been several close calls."}]},{"cues":[{"time":77413,"text":"But luckily, I'm an experimentalist at heart,"},{"time":81112,"text":"so I decided I would experiment"},{"time":84339,"text":"to try to find more optimal dosages"},{"time":86779,"text":"because there really isn't a clear road map"},{"time":88416,"text":"on this that's detailed."},{"time":90319,"text":"I began to try different mixtures,"},{"time":92470,"text":"and I was blown away by how"},{"time":95342,"text":"tiny changes in dosages"},{"time":97753,"text":"dramatically changed my sense of self,"},{"time":100902,"text":"my sense of who I was, my thinking,"},{"time":102713,"text":"my behavior towards people."},{"time":104972,"text":"One particularly dramatic case:"},{"time":107021,"text":"for a couple months I actually tried dosages"},{"time":108889,"text":"and chemicals typical of a man in his early 20s,"},{"time":112797,"text":"and I was blown away by how my thoughts changed."},{"time":115808,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":118928,"text":"I was angry all the time,"},{"time":121986,"text":"I thought about sex constantly,"},{"time":123832,"text":"and I thought I was the smartest person"},{"time":126781,"text":"in the entire world, and"},{"time":128832,"text":"—(Laughter)—"},{"time":131095,"text":"of course over the years I'd\nmet guys kind of like that,"},{"time":134020,"text":"or maybe kind of toned-down versions of that."},{"time":136287,"text":"I was kind of extreme."},{"time":138471,"text":"But to me, the surprise was,"},{"time":141040,"text":"I wasn't trying to be arrogant."},{"time":143206,"text":"I was actually trying,"},{"time":146415,"text":"with a little bit of insecurity,"},{"time":148775,"text":"to actually fix a problem in front of me,"},{"time":151775,"text":"and it just didn't come out that way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":153631,"text":"So I couldn't handle it."},{"time":155114,"text":"I changed my dosages."},{"time":156639,"text":"But that experience, I think, gave me"},{"time":159094,"text":"a new appreciation for men"},{"time":160845,"text":"and what they might walk through,"},{"time":162661,"text":"and I've gotten along with men"},{"time":164351,"text":"a lot better since then."}]},{"cues":[{"time":166190,"text":"What I was trying to do"},{"time":167735,"text":"with tuning these hormones"},{"time":169763,"text":"and neurotransmitters and so forth"},{"time":172086,"text":"was to try to get my intelligence back"},{"time":175691,"text":"after my illness and surgery,"},{"time":178325,"text":"my creative thought, my idea flow."},{"time":180960,"text":"And I think mostly in images,"},{"time":183601,"text":"and so for me that became a key metric --"},{"time":186453,"text":"how to get these mental images"},{"time":188783,"text":"that I use as a way of rapid prototyping,"},{"time":191287,"text":"if you will, my ideas,"},{"time":193030,"text":"trying on different new ideas for size,"},{"time":195402,"text":"playing out scenarios."},{"time":197097,"text":"This kind of thinking isn't new."},{"time":199010,"text":"Philiosophers like Hume and Descartes and Hobbes"},{"time":202265,"text":"saw things similarly."},{"time":203793,"text":"They thought that mental images and ideas"},{"time":206530,"text":"were actually the same thing."},{"time":208861,"text":"There are those today that dispute that,"},{"time":211278,"text":"and lots of debates about how the mind works,"},{"time":214473,"text":"but for me it's simple:"},{"time":216209,"text":"Mental images, for most of us,"},{"time":218741,"text":"are central in inventive and creative thinking."}]},{"cues":[{"time":222675,"text":"So after several years,"},{"time":224450,"text":"I tuned myself up and I have lots of great,"},{"time":227683,"text":"really vivid mental images with a lot of sophistication"},{"time":230731,"text":"and the analytical backbone behind them."},{"time":233000,"text":"And so now I'm working on,"},{"time":234921,"text":"how can I get these mental images in my mind"},{"time":239083,"text":"out to my computer screen faster?"},{"time":241933,"text":"Can you imagine, if you will,"},{"time":244022,"text":"a movie director being able to use"},{"time":246142,"text":"her imagination alone to\ndirect the world in front of her?"},{"time":249904,"text":"Or a musician to get the music out of his head?"},{"time":253492,"text":"There are incredible possibilities with this"},{"time":255784,"text":"as a way for creative people"},{"time":257777,"text":"to share at light speed."},{"time":260010,"text":"And the truth is, the remaining bottleneck"},{"time":262008,"text":"in being able to do this"},{"time":263181,"text":"is just upping the resolution of brain scan systems."}]},{"cues":[{"time":267161,"text":"So let me show you why I think \nwe're pretty close to getting there"},{"time":270029,"text":"by sharing with you two recent experiments"},{"time":272416,"text":"from two top neuroscience groups."},{"time":275003,"text":"Both used fMRI technology --"},{"time":277491,"text":"functional magnetic resonance imaging technology --"},{"time":279770,"text":"to image the brain,"},{"time":281181,"text":"and here is a brain scan set from Giorgio Ganis"},{"time":284438,"text":"and his colleagues at Harvard."},{"time":286388,"text":"And the left-hand column shows a brain scan"},{"time":289542,"text":"of a person looking at an image."},{"time":292809,"text":"The middle column shows the brainscan"},{"time":294738,"text":"of that same individual"},{"time":296359,"text":"imagining, seeing that same image."},{"time":299425,"text":"And the right column was created"},{"time":301473,"text":"by subtracting the middle \ncolumn from the left column,"},{"time":305083,"text":"showing the difference to be nearly zero."},{"time":308026,"text":"This was repeated on lots of different individuals"},{"time":310920,"text":"with lots of different images,"},{"time":313750,"text":"always with a similar result."},{"time":315354,"text":"The difference between seeing an image"},{"time":317443,"text":"and imagining seeing that same image"},{"time":319898,"text":"is next to nothing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":322053,"text":"Next let me share with you one other experiment,"},{"time":324814,"text":"this from Jack Gallant's lab at Cal Berkeley."},{"time":329355,"text":"They've been able to decode brainwaves"},{"time":331418,"text":"into recognizable visual fields."},{"time":333859,"text":"So let me set this up for you."},{"time":335164,"text":"In this experiment, individuals were shown"},{"time":337497,"text":"hundreds of hours of YouTube videos"},{"time":339492,"text":"while scans were made of their brains"},{"time":341531,"text":"to create a large library of their brain reacting"},{"time":344747,"text":"to video sequences."},{"time":347396,"text":"Then a new movie was shown with new images,"},{"time":350246,"text":"new people, new animals in it,"},{"time":352198,"text":"and a new scan set was recorded."},{"time":354909,"text":"The computer, using brain scan data alone,"},{"time":357697,"text":"decoded that new brain scan"},{"time":359721,"text":"to show what it thought the \nindividual was actually seeing."},{"time":364097,"text":"On the right-hand side, you\nsee the computer's guess,"},{"time":367478,"text":"and on the left-hand side, the presented clip."},{"time":371485,"text":"This is the jaw-dropper."},{"time":373804,"text":"We are so close to being able to do this."},{"time":376491,"text":"We just need to up the resolution."},{"time":379276,"text":"And now remember that when you see an image"},{"time":382528,"text":"versus when you imagine that same image,"},{"time":384686,"text":"it creates the same brain scan."}]},{"cues":[{"time":388161,"text":"So this was done with the highest-resolution"},{"time":390883,"text":"brain scan systems available today,"},{"time":393068,"text":"and their resolution has increased really"},{"time":394852,"text":"about a thousandfold in the last several years."},{"time":398349,"text":"Next we need to increase the resolution"},{"time":400671,"text":"another thousandfold"},{"time":402648,"text":"to get a deeper glimpse."},{"time":404437,"text":"How do we do that?"},{"time":405948,"text":"There's a lot of techniques in this approach."},{"time":408562,"text":"One way is to crack open your\nskull and put in electrodes."},{"time":411680,"text":"I'm not for that."},{"time":413083,"text":"There's a lot of new imaging techniques"},{"time":416038,"text":"being proposed, some even by me,"},{"time":418041,"text":"but given the recent success of MRI,"},{"time":421000,"text":"first we need to ask the question,"},{"time":423068,"text":"is it the end of the road with this technology?"},{"time":425909,"text":"Conventional wisdom says the only way"},{"time":428364,"text":"to get higher resolution is with bigger magnets,"},{"time":430953,"text":"but at this point bigger magnets"},{"time":432795,"text":"only offer incremental resolution improvements,"},{"time":436545,"text":"not the thousandfold we need."},{"time":438705,"text":"I'm putting forward an idea:"},{"time":440528,"text":"instead of bigger magnets,"},{"time":442491,"text":"let's make better magnets."},{"time":444941,"text":"There's some new technology breakthroughs"},{"time":446944,"text":"in nanoscience"},{"time":448401,"text":"when applied to magnetic structures"},{"time":450128,"text":"that have created a whole new class of magnets,"},{"time":453141,"text":"and with these magnets, we can lay down"},{"time":455672,"text":"very fine detailed magnetic field patterns"},{"time":457839,"text":"throughout the brain,"},{"time":459194,"text":"and using those, we can actually create"},{"time":462376,"text":"holographic-like interference structures"},{"time":465214,"text":"to get precision control over many patterns,"},{"time":468683,"text":"as is shown here by shifting things."},{"time":471128,"text":"We can create much more complicated structures"},{"time":474278,"text":"with slightly different arrangements,"},{"time":476349,"text":"kind of like making Spirograph."}]},{"cues":[{"time":479382,"text":"So why does that matter?"},{"time":481610,"text":"A lot of effort in MRI over the years"},{"time":484187,"text":"has gone into making really big,"},{"time":487024,"text":"really huge magnets, right?"},{"time":489634,"text":"But yet most of the recent advances"},{"time":492143,"text":"in resolution have actually come from"},{"time":494340,"text":"ingeniously clever encoding and decoding solutions"},{"time":498348,"text":"in the F.M. radio frequency transmitters and receivers"},{"time":501635,"text":"in the MRI systems."},{"time":504326,"text":"Let's also, instead of a uniform magnetic field,"},{"time":507648,"text":"put down structured magnetic patterns"},{"time":510320,"text":"in addition to the F.M. radio frequencies."},{"time":513419,"text":"So by combining the magnetics patterns"},{"time":515726,"text":"with the patterns in the F.M. radio frequencies"},{"time":518436,"text":"processing which can massively increase"},{"time":520607,"text":"the information that we can extract"},{"time":522576,"text":"in a single scan."},{"time":525022,"text":"And on top of that, we can then layer"},{"time":527354,"text":"our ever-growing knowledge \nof brain structure and memory"},{"time":531826,"text":"to create a thousandfold increase that we need."},{"time":535521,"text":"And using fMRI, we should be able to measure"},{"time":538464,"text":"not just oxygenated blood flow,"},{"time":540546,"text":"but the hormones and neurotransmitters \nI've talked about"},{"time":543447,"text":"and maybe even the direct neural activity,"},{"time":545792,"text":"which is the dream."}]},{"cues":[{"time":547295,"text":"We're going to be able to dump our ideas"},{"time":549529,"text":"directly to digital media."},{"time":552223,"text":"Could you imagine if we could leapfrog language"},{"time":554934,"text":"and communicate directly with human thought?"},{"time":559143,"text":"What would we be capable of then?"},{"time":562336,"text":"And how will we learn to deal"},{"time":564973,"text":"with the truths of unfiltered human thought?"},{"time":569192,"text":"You think the Internet was big."},{"time":571759,"text":"These are huge questions."},{"time":574361,"text":"It might be irresistible as a tool"},{"time":576509,"text":"to amplify our thinking and communication skills."},{"time":580385,"text":"And indeed, this very same tool"},{"time":582408,"text":"may prove to lead to the cure"},{"time":584534,"text":"for Alzheimer's and similar diseases."}]},{"cues":[{"time":587608,"text":"We have little option but to open this door."},{"time":591120,"text":"Regardless, pick a year --"},{"time":592705,"text":"will it happen in five years or 15 years?"},{"time":594971,"text":"It's hard to imagine it taking much longer."},{"time":599587,"text":"We need to learn how to take this step together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":603282,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":605456,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}